Delayed Grace				KEY:Chosen One ~ Delayed Grace			CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:Paladin Class Features.ChosenOneClassFeatures.SpecialQuality.Supernatural																																																																																																																	DESC:A chosen one begins her adventuring career without fully understanding her true potential. The chosen one uses the Barbarian, Rogue, Sorcerer column on Table 7-1 on page 169 of the Pathfinder RPG Core Rulebook to calculate her typical starting age.																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																												ABILITY:Special Ability|AUTOMATIC|Paladin ~ Smite Evil|PRECLASS:1,Paladin=1	ABILITY:Special Ability|AUTOMATIC|Paladin ~ Divine Grace|PRECLASS:1,Paladin=4																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																				SOURCEPAGE:p.6
Lay on Paws					KEY:Chosen One ~ Lay on Paws				CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:Paladin Class Features.ChosenOneClassFeatures.SpecialQuality.Supernatural																																																																																																																	DESC:A chosen one's familiar is able to borrow some of her divine energy to heal itself and others. The familiar can use the chosen one's lay on hands ability, including all of her mercies, but each such use consumes two uses of the paladin's lay on hands ability.	DESC:The familiar can also channel positive energy, but each such use consumes four uses of the paladin's lay on hands ability.|PRECLASS:1,Paladin=4	DESC:This ability alters lay on hands and channel positive energy.																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																		SOURCEPAGE:p.6
True Form					KEY:Chosen One ~ True Form				CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:Paladin Class Features.ChosenOneClassFeatures.SpecialQuality.Extraordinary																																																																																																																	DESC:A chosen one's familiar reveals its true form, transforming into an outsider improved familiar that matches the chosen one's patron's alignment (typically an arbiter, a cassisian, a harbinger, or a silvanshee, but potentially any lawful neutral, lawful good, or neutral good outsider familiar depending on the patron). The familiar gains the change shape universal monster ability if it doesn't already have it, which it can use at will to transform into its original form or back to its true form. [PCGen cannot force this change of familiar automatically. It must be done manually!!]																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																				ABILITY:FEAT|VIRTUAL|Improved Familiar																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																							SOURCEPAGE:p.6
