Familiar Adept				KEY:Wizard Archetype ~ Familiar Adept		CATEGORY:Archetype		TYPE:Archetype.WizardArchetype																																				PRECLASS:1,Wizard=1	PREMULT:1,[PREABILITY:1,CATEGORY=Archetype,Wizard Archetype ~ Familiar Adept],[!PREFACT:1,ABILITIES,Wizard_Archetype_ArcaneBond=True,Wizard_Archetype_ScribeScroll=True,Wizard_Archetype_BonusFeat5=True,Wizard_Archetype_BonusFeat10=True,Wizard_Archetype_SpellBook=True]																																DESC:Many wizards employ familiars to assist them, but only a few have unlocked the true power of their school of magic through the familiar itself.																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																														ABILITY:Wizard Class Feature|AUTOMATIC|Familiar Adept ~ School Familiar|PRECLASS:1,Wizard=1	ABILITY:Wizard Class Feature|AUTOMATIC|Familiar Adept ~ Familiar Spells|PRECLASS:1,Wizard=1	ABILITY:Wizard Class Feature|AUTOMATIC|Familiar Adept ~ Focused School|PRECLASS:1,Wizard=1																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																													COST:0	SOURCEPAGE:p.8																		FACT:Wizard_Archetype_ArcaneBond|true	FACT:Wizard_Archetype_ScribeScroll|true	FACT:Wizard_Archetype_BonusFeat5|true	FACT:Wizard_Archetype_BonusFeat10|true	FACT:Wizard_Archetype_SpellBook|true	FACT:Wizard_CF_BondedObject|true	FACT:Wizard_CF_ScribeScroll|true	FACT:Wizard_CF_BonusFeat5|true	FACT:Wizard_CF_BonusFeat10|true
Pact Wizard					KEY:Wizard Archetype ~ Pact Wizard			CATEGORY:Archetype		TYPE:Archetype.WizardArchetype																																				PRECLASS:1,Wizard=1	PREMULT:1,[PREABILITY:1,CATEGORY=Archetype,Wizard Archetype ~ Pact Wizard],[!PREFACT:1,ABILITIES,Wizard_Archetype_ArcaneBond=True,Wizard_Archetype_ArcaneSchool=True]																																																	DESC:Some wizards make bargains with beings from other realms in order to gain arcane power. These pact wizards have unparalleled access to extraplanar allies, but these bonds never come without strings attached.																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																			ABILITY:Wizard Class Feature|AUTOMATIC|Pact Wizard ~ Familiar|PRECLASS:1,Wizard=1	ABILITY:Wizard Class Feature|AUTOMATIC|Pact Wizard ~ Pact Focus|PRECLASS:1,Wizard=1	ABILITY:Wizard Class Feature|AUTOMATIC|Pact Wizard ~ Pact|PRECLASS:1,Wizard=1	ABILITY:Wizard Class Feature|AUTOMATIC|Pact Wizard ~ Aura|PRECLASS:1,Wizard=1	ABILITY:Wizard Class Feature|AUTOMATIC|Pact Wizard ~ Pact Summons|PRECLASS:1,Wizard=1	ABILITY:Wizard Class Feature|AUTOMATIC|Pact Wizard ~ True Form|PRECLASS:1,Wizard=7																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																										COST:0	SOURCEPAGE:p.8																		FACT:Wizard_Archetype_ArcaneBond|true	FACT:Wizard_Archetype_ArcaneSchool|true	FACT:Wizard_CF_BondedObject|true	FACT:Wizard_CF_ConjurationOppositionSchool|true
Spirit Binder				KEY:Wizard Archetype ~ Spirit Binder		CATEGORY:Archetype		TYPE:Archetype.WizardArchetype																																				PRECLASS:1,Wizard=1	PREMULT:1,[PREABILITY:1,CATEGORY=Archetype,Wizard Archetype ~ Spirit Binder],[!PREFACT:1,ABILITIES,Wizard_Archetype_ArcaneBond=True,Wizard_Archetype_ArcaneSchool=True,Wizard_Archetype_ScribeScroll=True,Wizard_Archetype_BonusFeats=True]																																					DESC:While most wizards learn their arts through gradual study, spirit binders have made a sudden arcane breakthrough due to the traumatic experience of losing a loved one.																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																										ABILITY:Wizard Class Feature|AUTOMATIC|Spirit Binder ~ Soulbound Familiar|PRECLASS:1,Wizard=1	ABILITY:Wizard Class Feature|AUTOMATIC|Spirit Binder ~ Lost Talents|PRECLASS:1,Wizard=1																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																													COST:0	SOURCEPAGE:p.9																		FACT:Wizard_Archetype_ArcaneBond|true	FACT:Wizard_Archetype_ArcaneSchool|true	FACT:Wizard_Archetype_ScribeScroll|true	FACT:Wizard_Archetype_BonusFeats|true	FACT:Wizard_CF_BondedObject|true	FACT:Wizard_CF_NecromancyOppositionSchool|true	FACT:Wizard_CF_ScribeScroll|true	FACT:Wizard_CF_BonusFeats|true

#Familiar Adept
School Familiar				KEY:Familiar Adept ~ School Familiar		CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:Wizard Class Feature.FamiliarAdeptClassFeatures.SpecialQuality.Extraordinary																																																																																																												DESC:A familiar adept must select a familiar for his arcane bond. His familiar automatically gains the school familiar archetype, but it cannot use its lesser school power until 4th level. At 8th level, it gains access to its greater school power. This ability alters arcane bond.																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																								ABILITY:FEAT|VIRTUAL|School Familiar	ABILITY:FEAT|VIRTUAL|Greater School Familiar|PRECLASS:1,Wizard=8																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																									BONUS:VAR|Pool_ArcaneOppositionSchool|1																																																																																																																												SOURCEPAGE:p.8
Familiar Spells				KEY:Familiar Adept ~ Familiar Spells		CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:Wizard Class Feature.FamiliarAdeptClassFeatures.SpecialQuality.Extraordinary																																																																																																												DESC:A familiar adept stores his spells in his familiar rather than in a spellbook, exactly as a witch does. His familiar can freely trade spells known with a witch's familiar, provided the spells traded are on both casters' class spell lists. The familiar adept's familiar uses the witch rules for familiars, including the increased cost of replacing the familiar. This ability alters spellbooks.																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																															SOURCEPAGE:p.8
Focused School				KEY:Familiar Adept ~ Focused School			CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:Wizard Class Feature.FamiliarAdeptClassFeatures.SpecialQuality.Extraordinary																																																																																																												DESC:A familiar adept's training is focused more deeply on his familiar and his school of magic. His familiar gains the ability to use the wizard's 1st-level school ability %1 times per day without it counting against the wizard's daily uses.|1+WizardLVL/5																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																							SOURCEPAGE:p.8

#Pact Wizard
Familiar					KEY:Pact Wizard ~ Familiar				CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:Wizard Class Feature.PactWizardClassFeatures.SpecialQuality.Extraordinary																																																																																																												DESC:A pact wizard must select a familiar for his arcane bond. The familiar's loyalty ultimately lies with the pact wizard's patron, and it reports back to the patron on the wizard's activities. This ability alters arcane bond.																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																												SOURCEPAGE:p.8
Pact Focus					KEY:Pact Wizard ~ Pact Focus				CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:Wizard Class Feature.PactWizardClassFeatures.SpecialQuality.Extraordinary																																																																																																												DESC:A pact wizard must choose one additional opposition school, even if he is a universalist. A pact wizard can't pick conjuration as an opposition school. This ability alters arcane school.																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																	BONUS:VAR|Pool_ArcaneOppositionSchool|1																																																																																																																												SOURCEPAGE:p.8
Pact						KEY:Pact Wizard ~ Pact					CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:Wizard Class Feature.PactWizardClassFeatures.SpecialQuality.Extraordinary																																																																																																												DESC:A pact wizard enters into a bargain with an extraplanar being in order to gain increased wizardly powers. At 1st level, he selects a patron belonging to one specific subtype of outsider for which there exists an improved familiar option (such as devil or azata). The pact wizard can select a subtype of outsider even with a diametrically opposed alignment; in this case, the patron being offers the pact in an attempt to tempt or redeem the pact wizard. A pact wizard whose alignment shifts away from the chosen outsider subtype, who grossly abuses his familiar or any outsider of the chosen subtype, or who commits egregious acts against the alignment of the patron loses all the benefits of this archetype (but keeps the additional opposition school) until he receives an atonement.																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																														SOURCEPAGE:p.8
Aura						KEY:Pact Wizard ~ Aura					CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:Wizard Class Feature.PactWizardClassFeatures.SpecialQuality.Extraordinary																																																																																																												DESC:A pact wizard has an aura corresponding to the alignment of his chosen subtype as a cleric of his wizard level.																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																														SOURCEPAGE:p.9
Pact Summons				KEY:Pact Wizard ~ Pact Summons			CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:Wizard Class Feature.PactWizardClassFeatures.SpecialQuality.Extraordinary																																																																																																												DESC:A pact wizard can select Sacred Summons (Ultimate Magic 155) as a wizard bonus feat. He can use this feat only to summon outsiders of his chosen subtype.																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																							SOURCEPAGE:p.9
True Form					KEY:Pact Wizard ~ True Form				CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:Wizard Class Feature.PactWizardClassFeatures.SpecialQuality.Extraordinary																																																																																																												DESC:A pact wizard's familiar reveals its true form, automatically transforming into an outsider improved familiar of the chosen subtype. [PCGen cannot force this change of familiar automatically. It must be done manually!!]																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																	ABILITY:FEAT|VIRTUAL|Improved Familiar																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																					SOURCEPAGE:p.9


#Spirit Binder
Soulbound Familiar			KEY:Spirit Binder ~ Soulbound Familiar		CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:Wizard Class Feature.PactWizardClassFeatures.SpecialQuality.Extraordinary																																																																																																												DESC:A spirit binder must select a familiar for his arcane bond. Unlike in a normal familiar-summoning ritual, a spirit binder created his special familiar through a dangerous ritual catalyzed by the death of a loved one. Before the loved one's spirit passed on to the Boneyard, the spirit binder was able to bind the spirit to an animal or vermin, which then became his familiar. A soulbound familiar's personality is that of the lost loved one, rather than a servant of the spirit binder. It can have any alignment, even one that is diametrically opposed to the spirit binder's. A soulbound familiar has the base attack bonus and base saving throws of the loved one's favored class (using the spirit binder's level as its level). If the loved one died before the beginning of the campaign, the spirit binder selects the familiar's favored class at 1st level and it cannot be changed. This ability alters arcane bond. [Altered Base Attack and Saves are NOT IMPLEMENTED!!]																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																															SOURCEPAGE:p.9
Lost Talents				KEY:Spirit Binder ~ Lost Talents			CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:Wizard Class Feature.PactWizardClassFeatures.SpecialQuality.Extraordinary																																																																																												DEFINE:WizardIsSoulBinder|0												DESC:A spirit binder's soulbound familiar possesses some of the ability of the lost loved one, and it is capable of learning more. At 1st level, 5th level, and every 5 levels thereafter, the spirit binder's familiar gains a new feat for which it meets the prerequisites.																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																			BONUS:VAR|WizardIsSoulBinder|0																																																																																																																												SOURCEPAGE:p.9

Soulbound Familiar Lost Talents	KEY:Soulbound Familiar ~ Lost Talents		CATEGORY:Internal			TYPE:SpecialQuality.Extraordinary																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																												ADD:FEAT|1+MasterLevel/5|ALL																																																																																																																																																												SOURCEPAGE:p.9

