Familiar Feat				KEY:Witch Hex ~ Familiar Feat				CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:WitchClassFeatures.SpecialQuality.Supernatural.WitchHex.MinorHex																																																																																																																			DESC:You may take a familiar feat in place of a hex.																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																							STACK:YES	MULT:YES	CHOOSE:NOCHOICE																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																			BONUS:ABILITYPOOL|Witch Familiar Feat Choice|1																																																																																																																																																				SOURCEPAGE:p.18
